                li.sidebar-nav-item
                    a(href='#about') About
                li.sidebar-nav-item
                    a(href='#blog') Blog
                li.sidebar-nav-item
                    a(href='#work') Work Exp.
                li.sidebar-nav-item
                    a(href='#connect') Connect

        // Header
        header.masthead.d-flex.align-items-center
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.text-start
                h4.mb-5.text-uppercase Ishtiaque Zafar
                h1.mb-5 { converting ideas into products }
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl(href='#about') Find Out More

        // About
        section#about.content-section.bg-dark
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.text-start.text-light
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center
                    .col
                        h6.mb-5.text-uppercase About Me
                        h1.mb-1 Staff Software Engineer
                        h1.mb-1 Blogger
                        h1.mb-5 Dreamer, doer, go-getter
                        p.text-justify
                            | I enable businesses. I transform ideas into products using my coding superpowers.
                            | I am capable of building highly scalable solutions powered by the cloud!
                            | I am pro-serverless and pro-automation. If there's something that can be automated,
                            | I'll do it! I have worked at several startups from early stage phases and lead them to new heights.
                            | I am not your average "developer", I am extremely passionate about my work and love what I do.
                            | I also try be a part of the local developer community. I conduct training sessions,
                            | attend meetups and conferences and have spoken at a few myself.
                    .col
                        div.image-holder
                            div.about-image

        // Blog
        section#blog.content-section
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-12.col-md-6.order-last.order-md-first
                        a.btn-outline-dark.no-hover-effects(href='https://medium.com/@ishtiaque/no-code-isnt-scalable-our-learnings-at-finn-going-from-1000-toward-100-000-car-subscriptions-ac98e752fc61' target='_blank')
                            .container.px-0.mb-5
                                h4 No-code isn’t scalable. Our learnings at FINN going from 1000 toward 100,000 car subscriptions
                        a.btn-outline-dark.no-hover-effects(href='https://medium.com/@ishtiaque/how-to-stay-ahead-of-errors-and-downtime-as-you-scale-up-your-business-92a0cb316995' target='_blank')
                            .container.px-0.mb-5
                                h4 How to stay one step ahead of errors and downtime as you scale up your business
                        a.btn-outline-dark.no-hover-effects(href='https://medium.com/@ishtiaque/conways-law-and-how-it-can-help-in-making-system-design-decisions-545cd5c278f8' target='_blank')
                            .container.px-0.mb-5
                                h4 Conway's law and how it can help in making system design decisions
                        a.btn-outline-dark.no-hover-effects(href='https://medium.com/@ishtiaque/why-i-dont-like-api-frameworks-together-with-serverless-39200063b4e0' target='_blank')
                            .container.px-0.mb-5
                                h4 Why I don’t like API frameworks together with Serverless
                        a.btn-outline-dark.no-hover-effects(href='https://medium.com/@ishtiaque/how-a-german-start-up-achieved-4-mn-arr-in-one-year-89fe123e0079' target='_blank')
                            .container.px-0.mb-5
                                h4 How A German Start-up Achieved 4 Mn € ARR In One Year
                        a.btn-outline-dark.no-hover-effects(href='https://medium.com/@ishtiaque/why-i-chose-to-be-a-software-developer-bb6f2b4f1442' target='_blank')
                            .container.px-0.mb-5
                                h4 Why I chose to be a Software Developer
                    .col-12.col-md-6.order-first.order-md-last
                        .container.px-0.mb-5.text-end
                            h6.mb-5.text-uppercase Blog
                            h1.mb-5 My latest thoughts
                            p.text-justify
                                | I write sometimes, about my experiences, observations and thoughts in general.
                                | Read them on
                                a.btn-link.text-dark(href="https://medium.com/@ishtiaque" target="_blank") Medium
                                | or
                                a.btn-link.text-dark(href="https://dev.to/ishtiaque" target="_blank") dev.to

        // Work
        section#work.content-section.bg-dark
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.text-start.text-light
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center
                    .col
                        h6.mb-5.text-uppercase Work
                        h1.mb-5 I &hearts; Software Engineering
                        p.text-justify
                            | I am currently working at FINN GmbH, a car-subscription startup based 
                            | out of Munich, Germany. I work there as a Staff Software Engineer.
                            | I love working with TypeScript and AWS and my expertise lies in designing backend systems.
                            | I come from India. My professional life started out in 2015 and I have worked in various Indian
                            | startups before joining FINN in May 2020. Starting at FINN, my main task was to analyze the 
                            | existing processes in subscription management and car delivery, and to automate them. Automated processes are one of the main USPs of FINN.
                            | As FINN grew, I moved on to a specific sub-team in Operations department: the Customer Product team,
                            | to focus on building better services for our customers and acheived a industry leading Net Promoter Score (NPS) of 75!
                            | My Team and I also built a multi-country (EU and US) backend system to help us scale from 10,000 to 100,000 car subscriptions.
                            | Joining FINN as an early employee and building its technology from the ground up has been such an immense learning,
                            | and I saw it rise at such an amazing pace! We achieved so many milestones: reaching 4m ARR in the first year itself to 100m Subscription ARR in less than three years!
                            | We were awarded the 
                            a.btn-link.text-light(href='https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/linkedin-top-startups-2022-zehn-junge-top-unternehmen-/?trackingId=Ig%2F24ukwLvv2yKHM7HlpBw%3D%3D' target='_blank')
                                | Top 10 Statups in Germany (in 2022 and 2021) by LinkedIn!
                        p.text-justify
                            | For a complete and detailed work history, please refer to my LinkedIn page.
                    .col
                        div.image-holder
                            div.work-image

        // Call to Action
        section.content-section#connect
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.text-center
                h1.mb-5 Got a great idea? Let's talk!
                p
                    | Message me on LinkedIn and I'll get back to you as soon as time allows me. I'm always  
                    | open to collaborations and opportunities. We could even talk about tech or you can show 
                    | me your cool weekend project.

        // Footer
        footer.footer.text-center
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                ul.list-inline.mb-5
                    li.list-inline-item
                        a.social-link.rounded-circle.text-white.mr-3(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/ishtiaquezafar/' target='_blank')
                            i.icon-social-linkedin
                    li.list-inline-item
                        a.social-link.rounded-circle.text-white.mr-3(href='https://twitter.com/ZafarIshtiaque' target='_blank')
